  Institute of Biomedical Imaging and Bioengineering (NIBIB) of the
  National Institutes of Health (NIH) under award R01EB026299, the
  National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke (NINDS) of the
  NIH under award RF1NS133972, and the Congressionally Directed Medical
  Research Programs (CDMRP) of the U.S. Department of Defense (DoD)
  under award HT9425-23-1-0149.</p>
</sec>
